	(46, 1, '2025-02-23 14:15:01', '2025-02-23 14:15:01', '{\n    "widget_block[2]": {\n        "value": {\n            "raw_instance": {\n                "content": "<!-- wp:search {\\"width\\":220,\\"widthUnit\\":\\"px\\"} /-->"\n            }\n        },\n        "type": "option",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2025-02-23 13:36:49"\n    },\n    "sidebars_widgets[sidebar-1]": {\n        "value": [\n            "block-2",\n            "block-3",\n            "block-4",\n            "block-12"\n        ],\n        "type": "option",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2025-02-23 13:36:49"\n    },\n    "widget_block[12]": {\n        "value": {\n            "raw_instance": {\n                "content": "<!-- wp:gallery {\\"linkTo\\":\\"none\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\\"><!-- wp:image {\\"id\\":8,\\"sizeSlug\\":\\"large\\",\\"linkDestination\\":\\"none\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\"wp-block-image size-large\\"><img src=\\"http://wp-project1.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/think.png\\" alt=\\"\\" class=\\"wp-image-8\\"/></figure>\\n<!-- /wp:image -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:image {\\"id\\":10,\\"sizeSlug\\":\\"large\\",\\"linkDestination\\":\\"none\\"} -->\\n<figure class=\\"wp-block-image size-large\\"><img src=\\"http://wp-project1.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/4.png\\" alt=\\"\\" class=\\"wp-image-10\\"/></figure>\\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->"\n            }\n        },\n        "type": "option",\n        "user_id": 1,\n        "date_modified_gmt": "2025-02-23 13:36:49"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9055b295-2ead-4284-b21a-42bc59491c13', '', '', '2025-02-23 14:15:01', '2025-02-23 14:15:01', '', 0, 'http://wp-project1.local/?p=46', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
	(48, 1, '2025-02-26 15:09:02', '2025-02-26 15:09:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To understand the new smart watched and other pro devices of recent focus, we should look to Silicon Valley and the quantified movement of the latest generation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apple’s Watch records exercise, tracks our moves throughout the day, assesses the amount of time we are stood up and reminds us to get up and move around if we have been sat for too long – let’s not forget Tim Cook’s “sitting is the new factor” line.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you’re tapping, scrolling, and swiping on your phone, you probably don’t give much thought to the fact that your apps are consuming electricity – just that they’re chipping away at your battery life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s&nbsp;<em>engaging</em>. It’s&nbsp;<strong>hopeful</strong>. It pushes the plot forward.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Only a quarter of young adults are financially literate. You don’t want to overwhelm them with terrible advice. Best to keep them on track.JOHN MCCARTHY</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before you click away, disappointed that I brought up something as practical and boring as time management, hear me out. My intent is not to crush your spirits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Scientists bid Goodbye to Virus With Latest Vaccine', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'scientists-bid-goodbye-to-virus-with-latest-vaccine__trashed', '', '', '2025-03-06 15:57:25', '2025-03-06 15:57:25', '', 0, 'http://wp-project1.local/?p=48', 0, 'post', '', 0),
	(49, 1, '2025-02-26 15:09:02', '2025-02-26 15:09:02', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To understand the new smart watched and other pro devices of recent focus, we should look to Silicon Valley and the quantified movement of the latest generation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apple’s Watch records exercise, tracks our moves throughout the day, assesses the amount of time we are stood up and reminds us to get up and move around if we have been sat for too long – let’s not forget Tim Cook’s “sitting is the new factor” line.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you’re tapping, scrolling, and swiping on your phone, you probably don’t give much thought to the fact that your apps are consuming electricity – just that they’re chipping away at your battery life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s&nbsp;<em>engaging</em>. It’s&nbsp;<strong>hopeful</strong>. It pushes the plot forward.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Only a quarter of young adults are financially literate. You don’t want to overwhelm them with terrible advice. Best to keep them on track.JOHN MCCARTHY</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before you click away, disappointed that I brought up something as practical and boring as time management, hear me out. My intent is not to crush your spirits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Scientists bid Goodbye to Virus With Latest Vaccine', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '48-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-02-26 15:09:02', '2025-02-26 15:09:02', '', 48, 'http://wp-project1.local/?p=49', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
