	(55, 1, '2025-02-26 15:16:09', '2025-02-26 15:16:09', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To understand the new smart watched and other pro devices of recent focus, we should look to Silicon Valley and the quantified movement of the latest generation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apple’s Watch records exercise, tracks our moves throughout the day, assesses the amount of time we are stood up and reminds us to get up and move around if we have been sat for too long – let’s not forget Tim Cook’s “sitting is the new factor” line.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you’re tapping, scrolling, and swiping on your phone, you probably don’t give much thought to the fact that your apps are consuming electricity – just that they’re chipping away at your battery life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s&nbsp;<em>engaging</em>. It’s&nbsp;<strong>hopeful</strong>. It pushes the plot forward.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Only a quarter of young adults are financially literate. You don’t want to overwhelm them with terrible advice. Best to keep them on track.JOHN MCCARTHY</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before you click away, disappointed that I brought up something as practical and boring as time management, hear me out. My intent is not to crush your spirits.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Greatness Awaits You</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The average U.S. iPhone owner uses 1-2 gigabytes of LTE data per month, according to some studies. That data comes at an energy cost that’s opaque, because we can’t see it directly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can’t look to your peers in the industry, because all they’re going to tell you is that they are killing it, crushing it, changing the world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Also Read</strong>:&nbsp;<a href="https://smartmag.theme-sphere.com/good-news/harley-davidson-bundle-of-joy-crafted-for-top-speed/#"><strong>Journey towards Design Perfection with Google Studio</strong></a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":651,"linkDestination":"custom"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image"><a href="https://smartmag.theme-sphere.com/good-news/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2021/01/Depositphotos_427179760_xl-2015-scaled.jpg"><img src="https://smartmag.theme-sphere.com/good-news/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2021/01/Depositphotos_427179760_xl-2015-1024x683.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-651"/></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Smart Tech just keeps getting Smarter.</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To its detractors, love at first sight must be an illusion – the wrong term for what is simply infatuation, or a way to sugarcoat lust.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Take a social media hiatus.</strong> According to a recent survey from Everyday Health, 60 to 70 percent of young adults say they check their social media platforms at least daily. Why not dial that back for the holidays?</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Stick to your new routine.</strong> It’s tempting to shake up your typical schedule when the holidays come around, but women’s health expert and BINTO founder Suzie Welsh emphasizes the importance of routine amid the revelry.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Be intentional about fitness.</strong> If working out is a de-stressor for you 365 days of the year, you want to make it a priority, no matter how crazy the holiday season gets.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The truth, of course, is that these people have been lying to you all along.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Harley Davidson: Bundle of Joy Crafted for Top Speed', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'harley-davidson-bundle-of-joy-crafted-for-top-speed__trashed', '', '', '2025-03-06 15:57:25', '2025-03-06 15:57:25', '', 0, 'http://wp-project1.local/?p=55', 0, 'post', '', 0),
